name: The tenth incarnation. Sloth.
description:
Woke up. For the first six months, I didn't get off my mother. Then, somehow, I managed to get down. I don't know why. It was better to be on Mom. I thought. I've been thinking a lot. Two stuck thoughts bothered me. In my dream I often saw a cave with drawings. I only woke up to eat and go to the toilet. I didn't like walking. And nothing special came of it.

One day torrential rains began. I slept and ate a lot. I went down less and less often. One day I went down and drowned. At the moment of death, I realized that two thoughts is too much. I had to think about one thing…
